data.description: Variance granted Detached. Welcome to this unique multi-family property featuring 2 homes tucked away on a quiet road spanning 5.23 acres of land in the Desirable West end of Ramona. Both permitted single-story dwellings on one lot.  Each home has its individual address, 17224 Rancho Suenos Dr, 2925 ESR, 3 BR 2 BA & 17220 Rancho Suenos Dr 875 ESF 2 BR 1 BA and is accessible via its own driveway. Enjoy the rich and picturesque views from the main house.  Relax in the open floor plan that tastefully combines the kitchen and living room area alongside the wet bar.  A perfect home for entertaining friends and family. Spacious Master Bedroom w/walk-in closet, jacuzzi spa bath & walk in shower. Outdoor fruit trees line the property featuring Pomegranate, Lemon, Pear, Orange and Apple trees. The landscape also features its own grape vine at the entrance of the main house. Solar Panels and a private well are just some of the sustainable perks these homes have to offer. Past Mount Woodson Castle and Golf Course in sought after West Ramona, Walk, ride your bike or horse down the street to enjoy Ramona's Grassland County Preserve with miles of groomed trails. Perfect opportunity for a large family with a desire for separate residences, or a rental property for additional income or to help with mortgage. Come See!
